pageProduct.name: SUP Shots Collagen Hair Skin & Nails 8x50ml Vials
pageProduct.description:
General Information

2500mg of Collagen, Biotin and Vitamin C & E for that everyday glow.

BEAUTY BEGINS WITHIN
It's time you turn the way you think about beauty upside down, or perhaps inside out (see what we did there). Collagen is one of the key building blocks of our skin that helps keep it smooth, plump and glowing. However, as the years go by, our body's natural production of collagen depletes and we start to see those dreaded signs of ageing. 

WHY SHOT SUP?
Drink your supplements on-the-go with our super shots. SUP contains 2500mg Collagen hydrolystate, Zinc, Vitamin C, Vitamin E and Biotin. SHOTSUP

Size: 8x50mL

KEY FEATURES

• Contains 2500mg Collagen per serve
• Help nourish the skin
• Help boost your Collagen supplies
• Shot your vitamins on-the-go

Warnings

The food is not a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and exercise program. Not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women. Should be used under medical or dietetic supervision. Do not use if tamper evidence seal is broken or missing. Store below 25?°C.

Ingredients

Water, Sweeteners (erythritol, steviol glycoside), Apple juice concentrate, Bovine collagen hydrolysate, Flavour (citric acid monohydrate), Stabiliser (HM pectin), Natural blueberry flavour, L-Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C), Natural grape flavour, DL-a-Tocopheryl acetate (Vitamin E), Zinc gluconate, Lycobeads S beadlets, B-carotene, Biotin.

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

SHOT 1 SUP (50mL) for that everyday beauty hit.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
